PSUEDOCODE

START

DISPLAY menu options 
Read user input

IF choice = 1
    Show shoes
IF choice = 2
    Ask for shoe, size, quantity
    Create order
IF choice = 3
    IF order exists
        Ask for date and time
    ELSE
        Show error
IF choice = 4
    IF order exists
        Show summary
    ELSE
        Show error
IF choice = 5
    IF order exists
        Save to file
    ELSE
        Show error
IF choice = 6
    Exit program

REPEAT until exit

END
